# Testing and Quality Assurance Rules

- Use Jest framework for unit and integration testing.
- Aim for at least 80% code coverage across all modules.
- Write tests covering:
  - Core business logic
  - API endpoints (controllers)
  - Service layer and integration points
- Tests should be clear, isolated, and maintainable.
- Use descriptive test case names in Korean.
- Run tests before each commit and CI pipeline.
- All test-related communication and comments should be in Korean.

